---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title='About us'>
  <div class='main'>
    <article
      ><h1>This is Punkt Studio</h1><p
        >Punkt Studio is love. Love has various dimensions and one of them
        relates to finding the right balance and functionality. We create
        interiors with the utmost attention to our clients’ needs and
        aspirations.</p
      ><p
        >To us, design is mostly a philosophy and a lifestyle. It breeds on
        imagination, on courage to test something new. Imagination is the key
        driver to accomplishing the basic human need for beauty.</p
      ><hr />
      <div class='vcard columns'>
        <div
          ><img src='/assets/polly.webp' alt='Polly' /><div
            class='vcard__content'
            ><p>Polly Georgieva</p><quote
              ><span
                >Every room needs a touch of black, just as it needs at least
                one antiques piece.</span
              > - Jan Showers</quote
            ></div
          ></div
        >
        <div
          ><img src='/assets/denitsa.webp' alt='Denitsa' /><div
            class='vcard__content'
            ><p>Denitsa Nikolova</p><quote
              ><span>An interior is the natural projection of the soul.</span> -
              Coco Chanel</quote
            ></div
          ></div
        >
      </div>
    </article></div
  >
</Layout>
<style lang='scss'>
  article > p {
    max-width: 80ch;
    line-height: 1.8em;
  }
  .vcard {
    isolation: isolate;
    & > div {
      --filter: blur(2px);
      --transform: scale(0.98) translateY(3%);
      --bg-color: hsl(0 0% 0% / 0.2);
      --blur: blur(2px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      box-shadow: 3px 3px 8px hsl(0 0% 0% / 0.1);
      position: relative;
      background-color: white;
      &:after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-color: var(--bg-color);
        rotate: 2deg;
        transform: var(--transform);
        filter: var(--blur);
        transform-origin: center;
        z-index: -1;
      }
      &:before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-color: var(--bg-color);
        rotate: -2deg;
        transform: var(--transform);
        filter: var(--blur);
        transform-origin: center;
        z-index: -1;
      }
      img {
        flex: 0 1 0px;
        max-height: 150px;
        aspect-ratio: 446 / 600;
        @media screen and (min-width: 756px) {
          max-height: 300px;
        }
      }
      & > .vcard__content {
        flex: 1 1 100%;
        display: flex;
        flex-flow: column;
        justify-content: space-around;
        height: 100%;
        padding: 1rem;
        quote {
          position: relative;
          color: rgb(113, 113, 113);
          line-height: 1.8em;
          //   span {
          //     background-color: #e3e3e3;
          //     padding: 0.3em;
          //   }
          &:after {
            content: '”';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0.3em;
            left: -0.2em;
            font-size: 8em;
            font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            mix-blend-mode: darken;
            color: var(--header-bg);
            opacity: 0.7;
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
</style>
